
Thu Aug 14 13:48:11 MET DST 1997
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Made changes to make loading of '.pjt' files more effecient.  Especially,
avoiding loading them before it is needed (i.e. when they become selected).

Added a few 'bringToFront' to solve the problem on NTI that
shift-doubleclicked windows were opened behind the originating browser.
However, these changes did not solve the problem.

