depUtils/depGraph to use new scanIncludes.

Tue Jun  3 10:09:41 METDST 1997
----------------------------------------------------------------------

'Close' menu item in the File menu is now only enabled when there are
more than one sep. browser opened (to avoid confusion between 'Close'
and Quit').

