Problem: uniqName generates entries with both ':' and '/' in them.

Wed Feb 19 12:15:51 MET 1997
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Corrected a bug in selectFragmentGroup that 'forgot' to test if the fg
did exist before attaching it to the project/group lists.

Thu Jan 23 11:51:41 MET 1997
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Corrected a bug in private/mpsGraammarUtils.bet that gave a
'Configuration Error' when the MBSgrammarExt file is parsed (should
just be ignored as a normal situation.

Sat Jan 18 18:02:26 MET 199
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Corrected bug in mpsGrammarUtils, that implied that Ymer went down
when the MBSgrammarsExt file does not exist.

Made changes to the browsers declaration, removing a virtual final
binding to another virtual.  As a result hereof, five (5) usages of
browsers.scan in ymerBody (and other files) had to be changes to use
explicit reference assignments to obtain the proper qualifications.
This change is done in order to try to avoid a strange Segmantation
Error, occuring nondeterministic when using Sif.

