Wed Nov 13 11:13:35 MET 1996

Ensured, that reparse in parseEditor saves the corrected file before
reparsing.

Corrected error in parseProjects.bet that made it impossble to define
projects containing groups.

Made all projects with subprojects appear as projectname/ (previous
