April 22, 1996:

Beginning support for changing what is displayed in view (4) in
sourcebrowser.  Not complete yet.
----------------------------------------------------------------------
April 19, 1996:

Added support for .html and .txt files:  

   .html files in a project are viewed in the help window.
   .txt files in a project are viewed (and editable) in a fileEdit window.

Starting a major revision of the internals of sourcebrowser.
